com.simplify.android.sdk.api
Class AsyncApiRequest<I,V,L extends ErrorHandler>

java.lang.Object
  
      com.simplify.android.sdk.api.AsyncApiRequest<I,V,L>
Type Parameters:
I - The input type holding parameters for the Simplify.com call
V - The return value, coming back from the Simplify.com call
L - The callback listener interface
public abstract class AsyncApiRequest<I,V,L extends ErrorHandler>
extends

Basis for making an asynchronous calls to the Simplify.com API. Derived Request objects need to be able to make the specific server calls, and map the return value to a call on the callback listener interface.
